description.en: EBSP team provides services on ICO launch, listing, financing, and fundraising. The company already carried out more than 20 blockchain projects and signed contracts for more than $4.000.000. EBSP token is based on ERC-20 standard, limited to 1 billion coins and is used as a payment for services within the EBSP network. You can already get EBSP coins on p2pb2b and start trading.
